---
title: Southeast Asian Sweet Chilli Chicken Bowl with Creamy Pear Slaw, Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: This saucy and sticky delight uses Southeast Asian spices and a sticky sauce to coat juicy chicken for abundant flavours you could only dream of. The pear slaw provides a refreshing crunch, and steamed jasmine rice acts as the perfect vehicle to soak up that sauce!
